&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://talboomerik.be/2012/01/16/taking-baby-steps/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Here&lt;/a&gt; you can find the details of the session&lt;/p&gt;</content>
